## Virtual Threads

Virtual threads won&#39;t really help with the mapping from `Stream&lt;CompletableFuture&lt;T&gt;&gt;` to `Stream&lt;T&gt;`. Though since your background tasks are I/O bound, using a virtual thread pool to execute said background tasks _might_ be beneficial.








